2931.Name: 2020 Pennsylvania Mega Match
2931.WaiverText:
BY ALLOWING MY NAME TO APPEAR ON Mid Atlantic High School Paddle League, I and my partner agree to abide by all rules of Mid Atlantic High School Paddle League . I do hereby and on behalf of myself and my partner, heirs and legal representatives release and forever discharge Mid Atlantic High School Paddle League of and from any and all claims and demands of every kind, nature and character which I or my partner may have or may hereafter acquire for any and all damages, losses or injuries which may be suffered or sustained by me or my partner. I and my partner also understand that any special medical needs remain the responsibility of the individual player.
I and my partner hereby grant Mid Atlantic High School Paddle League permission to use our likeness in photograph(s)/video in any and all of its media, publications, whether now known or hereafter existing, controlled by Mid Atlantic High School Paddle League, in perpetuity, and for other use by Mid Atlantic High School Paddle League.  I and my partner will make no monetary or other claim against Mid Atlantic High School Paddle League for the use of such photograph(s)/video.
